### 1. Get all products
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/admin/Products

### 2. Get all suppliers
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/admin/Suppliers

### 3. Get all customers
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/admin/Customers

### 4. Filter products by stock
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=year(orderDate) eq 2026

### 5. Order products by price
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/admin/Products?$orderby=price desc

### 6. Expand supplier details
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/admin/Products?$expand=supplier

### 7. Expand category details
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/admin/Products?$expand=category

### 8. Product Catalog Report
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/reports/ProductCatalog

### 9. Order Report
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/reports/OrderReport

### 10. Low Stock Alert
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/reports/LowStockAlert

### 11. Filter report
GET https://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/reports/OrderReport?$filter=status eq 'OPEN'

